249
00:21:35,458 --> 00:21:36,958
善悪の区別も付かないの？笑 はぁ。
Can't you even tell right from wrong? Haha, *sigh*.

250
00:21:36,958 --> 00:21:40,458
減点方式で取り巻く環境に巻かれて
Swept up by the surrounding environment in a demerit system

251
00:21:40,458 --> 00:21:42,958
生涯、痛い！痛い！痛い！も聞かれないわ！って
My whole life, saying 'It hurts! It hurts! It hurts!' won't even be heard!

252
00:21:42,958 --> 00:21:45,558
当然の報いにクラっ ちゃっ た
Getting dizzy from the natural retribution

253
00:21:59,458 --> 00:22:01,458
人は鏡なんです
