シャットダウンしても付き纏う
Even if I shut it down, it clings to me

256
00:22:04,958 --> 00:22:06,458
己の弱さが不甲斐ない
My own weakness is so pathetic

257
00:22:06,458 --> 00:22:09,458
全部 全部 アンタのせいって
Saying 'it's all, it's all your fault'

258
00:22:09,458 --> 00:22:11,458
反吐が出るくらいに止まんないわ
It won't stop, to the point of throwing up

259
00:22:11,458 --> 00:22:14,958
いっその事切り離せた方が楽なのにナ
It would be much easier if I could just cut it off completely

260
00:22:14,958 --> 00:22:19,458
大体アナタのコト アタシ ダイダイダイダイダイキライ
Basically, I hate hate hate hate hate everything about you

261
00:22:19,458 --> 00:22:22,958
omg情けない 最早バイバイバイバイバイしたい
OMG, how pathetic, I just want to say bye-bye-bye-bye-bye already

